{"tid":527552,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[Box Art 講故事] FOSTER TEAM","createTime":"2018-01-12T18:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T17:05:52.000Z","uid":37125,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"db22f39c590fc7e566c2d41c0fac08a1adf48344","tid":527552,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T18:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/a60ead6cc7600ccfaaa9ddeba921e3da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fa60ead6cc7600ccfaaa9ddeba921e3da.jpg&h=8f470015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DiacloneFosterTeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDiacloneFosterTeam&d=NH1cLd6b0HR8c04Itq7TQDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=83329136\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DiacloneFosterTeam</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">依個 Facebook page 會以小弟自制嘅 Box Art 嚟講故事.<br />\n故事係關於 DIACLONE  (地球防衛軍)  入面一個叫 FOSTER 嘅小隊, 點樣喺X港以寡敵眾同 WARUDER (幻亂誕) 軍團抗衡. 佢哋嘅目標就係將X港從 WARUDER 帝國手中解放出嚟.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/26116402_1570949912985664_8163475425502382664_o.jpg?oh=6c12f93428a30ed2e3452b9ecf709821&amp;oe=5AFE52B9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F26116402_1570949912985664_8163475425502382664_o.jpg%3Foh%3D6c12f93428a30ed2e3452b9ecf709821%26oe%3D5AFE52B9&h=61ba5967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">故事簡介</span><br />\n203X年，WARUDER 帝國又翻嚟搞鳩地球。自202X年以來，DIACLONE 都 BBQ 咗好耐，係時候又要出動保衛地球。<br />\n<br />\n當 DIACLONE 同 WARUDER 軍團喺世界各地開緊火之際，X港又再次發揮佢嘅世界仔精神，人哋喺出面為自己星球打到&quot;堪堪聲&quot;，佢哋就扮低B，將自己宣佈為中立地區，對地球戰事不干預，不聞不問。WARUDER 軍團終於都打到嚟X國，X國班&quot;領導&quot;知道X港嘅戰略價值唔細，加上眼紅X港成為中立地區之後過得好過俾自己管治嘅時候，於是就同 WARUDER 帝國講數，話X國會自動投降，想俾 WARUDER 帝國統治。而投誠嘅禮物就係X港。世事就係噉，多行不義必自斃。個&quot;自&quot;就係X港嘅自己人，X國。<br />\n<br />\n單眼佬都知如果X港落入咗 WARUDER 手中，戰況會變得更麻煩，更難打。有見及此，DIACLONE 下令喺各部隊入面東拼西湊一隊雜牌小隊出嚟應乎住，收集多啲 intel 先。等鬆動啲嗰陣就會調派支援過去幫拖。依隊雜牌小隊叫做 &quot;FOSTER&quot;，行動代號為&quot;獅奪龍珠&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==========================================================<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">至於咩係 DIACLONE?</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">DIACLONE 係 Takara 喺1980年推出去嘅約1/60嘅科幻戰爭玩具. DIACLONE 旗下嘅一條 line - Car-Robots, 就係而家大家所熟悉嘅 Transformers 變形金剛. 喺2015年, TakaraTomy 將 DIACLONE Reboot, 用舊有嘅 product 以更現代化, 更精細嘅 design 重新推出. <br />\n<br />\n經過重新 design 後, 新版 DIACLONE 系列入面每一個部件, 只要你諗到佢點用(玩), 就可以用自己嘅想像力, 想點砌就點砌. </span><br />\n<br />\nOfficial site:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fdiaclone%2F&d=NH1cLd6b0HR8c04Itq7TQDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e9500823\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/</a>"},{"pid":"95a157d4edc0ac691ce4c08dd49b87ae4e574172","tid":527552,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653c2e8339b97ceee83514f5b1ef3e1ac1df5361","tid":527552,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2fca9fb00e1011428c645676c069ba2c887b35","tid":527552,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662eb5762e5d8674898e39bc0c7d0dae8cf63f2a","tid":527552,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d42511745063598a7b9f700987ef0cee1706a3","tid":527552,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201